assed: full force reindex + post-scan embedding burst survived\n- resource-map.md not present. Skipping coverage gate.\n\n## Review Boundaries\n\n- Max iterations: 1\n- Convergence threshold: 0.10\n- Severity threshold: P2\n- Executor: cli-opencode model=deepseek/deepseek-v4-pro\n- Session: fanout-p020-deepseek-1-1781721166412-nlwse6 (fan-out lineage)\n\n## What Worked\n\n_(pending first iteration)_\n\n## What Failed\n\n_(pending first iteration)_\n\n## Exhausted Approaches\n\n_(none yet)_\n\n## Ruled Out Directions\n\n_(none yet)_\n\n## Next Focus\n\nD1 Correctness: Verify that the reference-counted module's logic is correct, the embedding queue wiring respects the empty-queue guard, and the scan IIFE refactor preserves prior behavior.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p020-deepseek-1/deep-review-strategy.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p020-deepseek-1/deep-review-strategy.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p020-deepseek-1/deep-review-strategy.md","time":{"start":1781721249986,"end":1781721249989}},"id":"prt_ed6dca0df0011CStOQKY1emH3a","sessionID":"ses_129248bb6ffe0oApRY3GmfXiL0","messageID":"msg_ed6dc97f2001id2WKIoqUFTzQR"}}
